title: Memtest 4.21 OSX
description:
Memtest OSX is simply the best ram-testing utility for the Mac with the ability to find intermittent memory problems that are the frequent cause of unexplained crashes and freezes. Memtest can identify random memory problems that commercially available utilities miss including defective motherboard CPU cache memory.

Memtest is distributed as a universal (fat) binary containing four separate binary executables targeting each of the currently available Mac platforms. The appropriate machine-specific executable is loaded by OS X at launch time.
